2026-05-17T06:33:00.7456909Z 13    <!--
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7457501Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7458403Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7459584Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7460524Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7461543Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
