2026-05-17T06:33:00.7512592Z 37    <!--
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7513379Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-17T06:33:00.7514290Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
