2026-05-17T06:33:00.8501656Z 272        <!--
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8502274Z 273            Same hardening for Glance's InvisibleActionTrampolineActivity.
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8503380Z 274            The library entry is singleInstance with its own taskAffinity
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8504218Z 275            but omits excludeFromRecents (unlike its sibling
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8505014Z 276            ActionTrampolineActivity which already has it). When the
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8505876Z 277            process dies before the trampoline finishes, the system can
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8506720Z 278            restore the task from Recents and replay onCreate with a
2026-05-17T06:33:00.8507861Z 279            stale Intent whose ACTION_INTENT extra is missing — which
