2026-05-17T06:33:01.2510831Z 12    <!--
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2511232Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2511564Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2512220Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2512580Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2512971Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
