2026-05-17T06:33:01.2546270Z 21    <!--
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2546646Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2546828Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2547184Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2547508Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2547843Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2548171Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2548517Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2548847Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2549202Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2549509Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-17T06:33:01.2549656Z 32    -->
